text: Abdoulaye Djiba is a judoka from Senegal. Djiba competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and the 1976 Summer Olympics. He was born on 7 July 1938.Abdoulaye Djiba == References == Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Senegalese judoka Category:Olympians for Senegal
title: Abdoulaye Djiba
